1
00:02:22,900 --> 00:02:27,200
Puja e sotme eshte e Vishnumaya,

2
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:29,900
qe ishte motra e Shri Krishnas,

3
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:36,800
s'ishte planifikuar si nje puja

4
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,700
nderkombetare qe ne bejme.

5
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:42,800
Por thone se per dashurine e Zotit

6
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:50,300
kur te gjithe adhuruesit mblidhen,

7
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:54,700
Zoti gjithashtu duhet te thyeje shume rregulla,

8
00:02:55,500 --> 00:03:01,500
dhe keshtu u pranua te behej kjo puja.

9
00:03:01,900 --> 00:03:05,900
Mendoj se te pakten duhej bere nje here, ishte ide e mire.

10
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,100
Prej dashurise suaj

11
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:15,200
dhe perkushtimit tuaj u deshirua,

12
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:20,000
dhe keshtu kjo puja do te performohet.

13
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:23,900
Eshte thjesht spontane

14
00:03:24,300 --> 00:03:28,000
qe ndodhi qe une te jem ne kete kohe ne Angli,

15
00:03:28,300 --> 00:03:30,900
sepse nese do te ndodhte ndonjehere kjo puja,

16
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,800
duhej te ndodhte ne Indi.

17
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:39,100
Sepse kjo eshte puja per nje hyjni,

18
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,200
Vishnumaya,

19
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:49,000
fara e se ciles nuk eshte e lehte te mbillet

20
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:51,900
ne vendet perendimore.

21
00:03:54,300 --> 00:03:59,800
Tani i gjithe programimi shakti eshte kryer

22
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:05,800
ne nje menyre te tille qe ne kemi Nenen si Shakti sa per fillim,

23
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:11,400
Pastaj kemi tre shakti qe dalin prej Saj,

24
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:14,100
sic e dini - Mahakali, Mahalakshmi, Mahasaraswati.

25
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:19,400
Dhe me pas kemi femije prej tyre:

26
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,200
motra dhe vellezer.

27
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:27,800
Pra para se fuqia

28
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:31,400
e asaj qe ne e quajme gruaja ose bashkeshortja te krijohej,

29
00:04:31,900 --> 00:04:34,100
ishte fuqia e motres qe u krijua.

30
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:38,200
Pra, sic e dini qe u linden Brahma, Vishnu, Mahesha

31
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,900
per keto tre Shakti,

32
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:42,200
dhe te gjithe kishin motra.

33
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,500
Dhe motrat e tyre ishin te martuara

34
00:04:46,900 --> 00:04:52,400
- si Motra e Vishnus eshte Parvati

35
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:55,500
dhe Ajo ishte e martuar me Shiva.

36
00:04:54,553 --> 00:04:56,011
Nenen e Hershme.

37
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,500
Eshte shume e rendesishme per tu kuptuar

38
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:02,400
qe keto tre lloj fuqish

39
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:06,900
gjithmone luajne ne cakra.

40
00:05:07,300 --> 00:05:09,400
Dhe nese ju i kuptoni keto tre fuqi,

41
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:10,800
si ato luajne,

42
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,500
atehere do te kuptoni

43
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:16,400
cila eshte rendesia e Vishnumaya.

44
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:21,800
Vishnumaya eshte cilesia e motres ne nje familje.

45
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:26,700
Pra femra eshte fuqia.

46
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:31,300
dhe mashkulli eshte fuqia kinetike

47
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:35,800
qe thekson fuqite

48
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:41,600
e ketyre tre fuqive qe e rrethojne ate.

49
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:45,900
Pra kur vjen fuqia mashkullore,

50
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:48,700
gjithe keto fuqi behen

51
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:56,500
bashkepunetore te dobishme ne veprim me ate fuqi.

52
00:05:57,800 --> 00:06:01,400
Tani fuqia e Vishnumaya eshte shume e rendesishme per t'u kuptuar,

53
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:04,800
sepse fuqia e Nenes eshte per te mbrojtur pafajesine tuaj,

54
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:07,000
sepse kjo eshte gjeja me e rendesishme.

55
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:10,300
Fuqia e Nenes eshte per te mbrojtur pafajesine tuaj.

56
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:16,000
Tani, fuqia e Vishnumayas eshte per te mbrojtur dliresine tuaj.

57
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:21,600
Ndonjehere ju s'e kuptoni cfare eshte dliresia

58
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:24,100
dhe cfare eshte pafajesia.

59
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:28,900
Pafajesia eshte nje fuqi e cila nuk eshte e aktivizuar.

60
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:31,600
Sic kemi elektricitetin ne shtepine tone,

61
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:36,500
elektreciteti ekziston si pafajesia qe gjendet brenda nesh;

62
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:43,000
por miratimi (dekretimi) i saj eshte bere permes dliresise.

63
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:45,000
Nje person mund te thote,

64
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:48,400
"E bera shume pafajesisht"- jo s'mundet.

65
00:06:48,900 --> 00:06:51,400
Sepse cfaredo te beni nese eshte e pafajshme,

66
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:54,300
s'mund te jete e demshme per karakterin tuaj,

67
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:58,900
per pafajesine tuaj ose per drejtesine tuaj.

68
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:01,000
Pra keta njerez qe thone keshtu,

69
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:03,600
qe "E bera pafajesisht" e kane gabim,

70
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:07,900
sepse nese ben ndonje gje pafajesisht ajo shnderrohet ne dliresi.

71
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:12,800
Pra kur pafajesia eshte e praktikuar shnderrohet ne dliresi.

72
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:17,100
Ju duhet te keni respekt per dliresine tuaj.

73
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:21,500
Dliresia eshte ajo qe eshte fuqia e Vishnumaya brenda nesh,

74
00:07:21,500 --> 00:07:24,300
fuqia e Gauri, eshte virgjeri e paster.

75
00:07:24,300 --> 00:07:26,000
Ajo nuk martohet.

76
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,900
Sic e dini qe kur Vishnumaya u krijua,

77
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:34,100
sapo pas lindjes se Saj Ajo u vra nga Kamsa.

78
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:40,500
Tani per te kuptuar rendesine e dliresie brenda nesh,

79
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:44,000
ne duhet te dime qe dliresia eshte themeli

80
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:45,900
i te gjithe dharmave.

81
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:48,700
Vetem dhe derisa te keni sensin e dliresise

82
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:50,500
ju s'mund te keni dharma.

83
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:54,100
Dharma eshte e pamundur sepse ajo eshte themeli.

84
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:56,700
Do te jete nje shtepi e kartave;

85
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:00,600
nese nuk keni themelin e dliresise

86
00:08:00,900 --> 00:08:03,900
ajo thjesht do te rrezohet.

87
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:07,400
Pra dliresia eshte nje shume shume e rendesishme

88
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:10,000
e qe ka qene e sfiduar gjate ne Perendim,

89
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:12,300
dhe prandaj po them qe eshte e veshtire

90
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:14,700
per te mbjelle faren e dliresise ne kete vend.

91
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:16,200
Dhe kjo duhet te ndodhe,

92
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:19,500
mendoj duhet te kete nje plan hyjnor,

93
00:08:19,500 --> 00:08:23,000
qe po ndodh qe kjo puja e madhe

94
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,200
duhej te jepej ketu.

95
00:08:24,400 --> 00:08:26,000
Nuk eshte nje puja e lehte per t'u bere

96
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,300
- eshte per t'u bere nga njerez qe jane te pafajshem,

97
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:31,800
per t'u bere nga njerez qe kane ndjekur nje jete shume religjioze;

98
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,500
ata te cilet kane qene shume te dliret,

99
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:35,500
qe e kane respektuar dliresine e tyre.

100
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:37,000
Por tani meqe ju jeni shenjtore,

101
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:41,300
cdo gje para jush eshte e paster dhe e mire,

102
00:08:41,300 --> 00:08:44,500
sepse tani ju keni ndjekur nje jete shenjtori.

103
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:48,500
Prandaj dliresia eshte zgjuar brenda jush,

104
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:52,300
dhe dliresia punon tek ju si Gauri, si kundalini juaj.

105
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:57,800
Pra nese vini ne thelbin e jetes religjioze,

106
00:08:58,100 --> 00:09:02,200
e jetes se drejte, e jetes Sahaja Yoga, eshte dliresi.

107
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,200
Nuk mund ta tjetersosh ate.

108
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:10,500
Tani kjo dliresi ju jep juve maryadas,

109
00:09:10,800 --> 00:09:12,100
do te thote ju cakton kufijte.

110
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,300
(i drejtohet dikujt ne publik- Pse jeni ulur ketu?

111
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:21,300
Shkoni me tej, eshte me mire te jeni ne balle.

112
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:23,200
Kjo eshte - ju nuk jeni duke bere puja.

113
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,300
Nese jeni duke bere puja, atehere uluni ketu.

114
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:27,100
Perndryshe, me mire uluni.

115
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:28,900
Me mire t'i merrni vibrimet e Mia atje,

116
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:31,400
ne balle. Ketu, ejani.)

117
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:39,900
Pra dliresia eshte ajo qe ju jep maryadas,

118
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,800
ju jep kufij.

119
00:09:42,100 --> 00:09:43,800
Si ju jep kufij?

120
00:09:44,500 --> 00:09:48,300
Si, ne qiell ka vetetime.

121
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:52,500
Kur dy rete,

122
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,000
qe mund te themi jane si Sahaja yogis,

123
00:09:55,300 --> 00:09:59,500
dalin nga deti

124
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,300
dhe kane uje te paster

125
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:12,000
atje ne, keto re,

126
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:14,900
dhe ato duhet ta derdhin;

127
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:20,300
kur afrohen se bashku

128
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,600
dhe kapercejne limitet e egos se tyre,

129
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:27,800
ose luftojne me njera tjetren apo ne nje menyre perplasen,

130
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:31,700
eshte, aty ka dliresi,

131
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:34,200
ne kete vetetime  qe bie.

132
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:38,400
Kjo drite e cila te thote qe

133
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:41,700
"E ke gabim. Pse je duke luftuar nder vete?

134
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:44,200
Pse jeni duke kaluar egon e njeri-tjetrit?"

135
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:46,000
Kjo eshte puna e motres.

136
00:10:46,300 --> 00:10:48,500
Dje kemi patur shume motra.

137
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:51,400
Tani detyra e motres nuk eshte te mbaje anen,

138
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,700
por per te treguar nese i kalon kufijte e tu

139
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:56,200
te vellazerise,

140
00:10:56,500 --> 00:10:59,300
atehere do te kete nje vetetime(drite).

141
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:03,100
Tani kjo fuqi e vetetimes

142
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:07,200
eshte pjese e fuqise se Shri Krishna

143
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:09,800
te cilen Ai e nxorri nga Vetja e Tij.

144
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:13,700
Prandaj Ai u be kaq i embel,

145
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:18,200
misherim i bute (ndjeshem).

146
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,400
Ai e nxorri.

147
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:21,200
Ai tha, "Tani ti je bere motra Ime,

148
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:25,900
dhe sa here qe ata sillen keq me ty ben mire ta perdoresh.

149
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:31,000
Keshtu Shri Krishna u be kaq i sjellshem dhe shume,

150
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:34,600
sic e quajne misherim romantik;

151
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:38,200
sepse Ai nxorri vecmas pjesen moterore

152
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:40,000
dhe e vuri ne pune.

153
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,700
Por ajo ishte gjithmone me Te

154
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:43,900
dhe Ajo punoi me Te;

155
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:46,000
sepse ne familje motra

156
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:48,700
duhet te kuptoje te mos zihet me vellezerit,

157
00:11:49,100 --> 00:11:50,800
se duhet te kujdeset per ta,

158
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:53,600
qe ata te mos sfidohen (kundershtohen) nga te tjeret,

159
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:55,900
pra ajo u jep atyre maryadas

160
00:11:55,900 --> 00:12:00,000
sa larg te shkojne - sa larg te shkojne.

161
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:02,000
Tani eshte shume e rendesishme,

162
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:05,600
shume, shume e rendesishme per te gjithe ne te kuptojme

163
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:10,600
qe Frojdi dhe gjithe njerezit e paarsyeshem

164
00:12:10,900 --> 00:12:17,600
nxorren teorite per te sfiduar Vishnumaya,

165
00:12:19,100 --> 00:12:26,100
qe ne ke te kemi gjithe keto lloje qesharake marrdheniesh,

166
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:28,500
e cila eshte e pamundur,

167
00:12:28,900 --> 00:12:30,100
eshte dicka e gabuar.

168
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:33,700
Tani nese ka nje marrdhenie te tille

169
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:38,300
midis vellait dhe motres,

170
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:43,000
familja vuan per shtate breza

171
00:12:43,300 --> 00:12:46,400
nga semundje te tmerrshme - shtate brezash.

172
00:12:49,900 --> 00:12:53,700
Por nese ka nje tjeter marrdhenie te stilit Frojd,

173
00:12:53,700 --> 00:12:58,100
atehere familjes i duhet te vuaje per katermbedhjete breza.

174
00:12:59,300 --> 00:13:03,700
Pra forcat kufizuese te Vishnumaya jane te tilla

175
00:13:03,900 --> 00:13:07,600
qe egoja juaj eshte e kontrolluar, superegoja juaj eshte e kontrolluar,

176
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:10,300
familja juaj eshte e kontrolluar.

177
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:12,700
Cdokush eshte nen kontroll,

178
00:13:12,900 --> 00:13:17,500
nen drejtimin e kesaj fuqie te paster te Vishnumaya

179
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:20,700
qe ndodhet brenda secilit prej nesh.

180
00:13:22,100 --> 00:13:24,200
Dhe pjesa me e trishtueshme eshte qe

181
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,900
ne te gjitha vendet Perendimore

182
00:13:25,900 --> 00:13:29,500
Vishnumaya eshte e semure, absolutisht e semure.

183
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:32,100
Dua te them, madje kam humbur edhe Degjimin,

184
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:34,500
ka ardhur deri ne kete pike,

185
00:13:34,900 --> 00:13:36,100
ne anen e majte,

186
00:13:36,100 --> 00:13:41,500
sepse ndjenja e dliresise mungon teresisht.

187
00:13:42,900 --> 00:13:44,900
Tani duhet t'i harrojme njerezit

188
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:49,000
qe nuk kane fare arsye, tani ne jemi Sahaja yogis.

189
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:52,300
Pra te vijme ne piken e duhur, ne duhet te themi qe,

190
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:56,700
akoma shume njerez kane mbetur me ide qesharake,

191
00:13:57,000 --> 00:14:00,000
si "Kam marrdhenie  te mire me ate zoteri"

192
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:03,000
ose "Jam shume miqesore me kete apo ate zoteri"

193
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,200
dhe gjithe keto.

194
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:06,100
Pra nuk eshte nje maryada.

195
00:14:06,900 --> 00:14:12,500
Ju s'mund te keni miqesi me - ndermjet nje burri dhe gruaje,

196
00:14:12,500 --> 00:14:16,200
s'mundeni, eshte absurde absolutisht.

197
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:18,400
Ne Perendim e gjithe kultura eshte qesharake;

198
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:20,300
sepse nese shkon ne nje darke

199
00:14:20,300 --> 00:14:22,200
supozohet te uleni me burrin e dikujt

200
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:24,500
ne te dyja anet - e tmerrshme!

201
00:14:25,300 --> 00:14:28,200
Por ne Lindje, nuk behet,

202
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:32,500
sepse Vishnumaya eshte kunder ketyre gjerave.

203
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:36,300
Ajo do shohe qe gra e burra ulen se bashku.

204
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:41,500
Tani ketu, ju e dini qe pjesa e dliresise

205
00:14:41,900 --> 00:14:43,100
mungon kaq shume

206
00:14:43,100 --> 00:14:45,200
sa Vishudhet tuaja te majta po kapen (kane ngerce).

207
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:48,300
Dhe kur flas rreth tij, kap edhe me shume.

208
00:14:49,500 --> 00:14:51,100
Tani kur ju thoni nuk jam fajtor,

209
00:14:51,100 --> 00:14:54,100
ju ne fakt po e pranoni ndaj Vishnumayas,

210
00:14:54,300 --> 00:14:55,300
ndaj motres suaj,

211
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:58,900
duke i thene "Une nuk jam fajtor."

212
00:14:58,900 --> 00:15:02,100
Por Ajo nuk pelqen te kete faj mbi ju.

213
00:15:02,100 --> 00:15:04,500
Gruas mund t'i pelqeje qe ju te keni faj

214
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:06,600
Asaj mund t'i pelqeje qe ju  ta keni fajin,

215
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:09,200
sepse mendon qe po i sfidohet fuqia

216
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:13,200
dhe qe ka dike qe eshte kundershtari i saj.

217
00:15:13,500 --> 00:15:17,100
Por jo Vishnumaya, jo;

218
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:19,900
motra nuk e thote kete.

219
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:24,000
Por nje vella e moter nuk jane kurre miq.

220
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:27,000
Tani jemi ulur grup ketu.

221
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:31,300
Keshtu, ne cdo grup ka nje moter e vella,

222
00:15:31,800 --> 00:15:35,000
ata e dine qe jane (ekzistojne) si vellezer e motra

223
00:15:35,300 --> 00:15:37,100
por ata nuk kapen pas nje personi,

224
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:38,500
ata nuk i flasin ndonje personi,

225
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:41,500
ata s'behen miqesore me ate moter.

226
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:45,700
Si dikur ne patem nje fat te madh me keta te Krishtere,

227
00:15:45,900 --> 00:15:48,300
Kujtoj qe mund te kem patur te pakten

228
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:52,700
tridhjete kusherira dhe kater, pese vellezer ne ate kohe.

229
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:55,800
Dhe shkuam ne ate ngjarje,

230
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:57,400
dhe midis indianeve te krishtere

231
00:15:57,700 --> 00:16:01,800
ne kemi te Krishtere prej gjithe llojeve te shtresave.

232
00:16:02,100 --> 00:16:06,300
Keshtu atje ishin disa vagabonde,

233
00:16:06,300 --> 00:16:08,800
ato hodhen ca fjale rreth nesh,

234
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:10,800
ne motrave, kuptoni.

235
00:16:11,900 --> 00:16:13,500
Ne s'e dinim qe kishim kaq shume kusherinj.

236
00:16:13,900 --> 00:16:17,000
Ata kercyen perpjete, si me suste (jack-in-the-box lloj lodre)

237
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:21,300
i nxorren te gjithe e nisen t'i rrihnin ata djem.

238
00:16:21,500 --> 00:16:24,000
Atehere e kuptuam se sa shume kusherinj kishim.

239
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,500
Ndryshe nuk do ta dinim kurre;

240
00:16:25,500 --> 00:16:28,000
ata ishin diku, ne s'u folem shume atyre,

241
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:30,300
po flisnim me njera-tjetren, miqve tane,

242
00:16:30,300 --> 00:16:32,100
vajza qe flisnin me njera-tjetren.

243
00:16:32,100 --> 00:16:34,200
Papritur kuptuam sa shume kusherinj kishim

244
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:36,900
dhe sa vellezer. Ishte mjaft e papritur

245
00:16:37,200 --> 00:16:39,300
qe ne te kishim kaq shume kusherinj atje

246
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:40,400
dhe ne s'e dinim.

247
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:43,200
Menjehere ata u hodhen ne mbrojtje

248
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:45,800
te dliresise se motres se tyre,

249
00:16:45,800 --> 00:16:48,900
sepse ajo eshte baza e dliresise se tyre.

250
00:16:50,300 --> 00:16:54,800
Por normalisht ju nuk i flisni shume vellait,

251
00:16:55,300 --> 00:16:58,800
as vellai nuk ju flet ju shume,

252
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,300
ju nuk beheni miqesore.

253
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:03,700
Por ne kohen e veshtiresive, ne kohen e maryadas,

254
00:17:03,900 --> 00:17:09,000
ne kohen e te konsultuarit per dicka

255
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:11,900
qe eshte e shtrenjte ne familje, vjen motra.

256
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:14,500
Kohet e fundit vellaim Im, me i vogel,

257
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:15,500
Me shkroi nje leter

258
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:17,500
sepse kishte nje problem ne familje.

259
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:21,900
Tani nena Ime s'eshte atje, dhe normal qe nje moter eshte me mire

260
00:17:22,200 --> 00:17:26,800
sepse ajo eshte me lehte e gatshme ndaj teje se mamaja.

261
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:28,500
Nena eshte kaq e zene me te gjithe familjen,

262
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:30,100
gjithe punen, ju e dini cfare ben.

263
00:17:30,100 --> 00:17:33,300
Keshtu qe ndjenja moterore eshte shume e rendesishme.

264
00:17:33,500 --> 00:17:37,900
Tani vetem mendoni qe Vishuddhi jone i majte eshte shume keq.

265
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:45,400
Sigurisht qe eshte,

266
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:47,800
sepse nuk jemi kujdesur kurre per dliresine tone,

267
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:50,600
nuk e kemi respektuar dliresine tone.

268
00:17:51,100 --> 00:17:53,100
Ne Indi nuk ndodh keshtu.

269
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:57,900
Gra dhe burra e respektojne shume dliresine e tyre.

270
00:17:58,300 --> 00:18:01,000
Dhe pyeta disa djem qe kishin shkuar jashte,

271
00:18:01,300 --> 00:18:03,700
thane qe "Pavaresisht se ishim duke gabuar

272
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:06,500
ne ato qe po benim, gjithe kohes ne e dinim disi

273
00:18:06,900 --> 00:18:08,300
qe po gabonim."

274
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:09,300
I them, "Si keshtu?"

275
00:18:09,300 --> 00:18:12,300
Ai thote, "Ka dicka si marrdhenie me motren."

276
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:19,000
Por mund te them tani qe burrat Indiane jane bere

277
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,500
tamam si ju,

278
00:18:20,700 --> 00:18:23,800
dhe e kane humbur fuqine e tyre per te mbajtur dliresine e tyre.

279
00:18:24,100 --> 00:18:26,600
Burrat duhet ta ruajne dliresine e tyre,

280
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:31,500
sepse ata mendojne se nuk i detyrohen asgje dliresise.

281
00:18:32,100 --> 00:18:38,600
Dhe nese thelbi i ekzistences suaj shpirterore

282
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:41,800
nuk ekziston, ju do humbisni ne kohe.

283
00:18:43,300 --> 00:18:45,200
Prandaj e kam thene shume here qe

284
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:49,300
vijeni vemendjen tek Nena Toke, gjelberim.

285
00:18:49,700 --> 00:18:50,900
Gjelberimi eshte ngjyra,

286
00:18:50,900 --> 00:18:53,000
nese e vini vemendjen tek ajo

287
00:18:53,300 --> 00:18:57,100
me pas do te shpetoheni

288
00:18:57,600 --> 00:19:01,300
nga keto gabime te shkeljes se kurores

289
00:19:01,300 --> 00:19:03,000
gjithe kohes,

290
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:05,300
shikoni motrat e te tjereve,

291
00:19:05,600 --> 00:19:08,500
grate e te tjereve, vajzat e te tjereve.

292
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:11,000
Pra marrdhenia

293
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:13,700
qe po shprehet tani, sic e dini,

294
00:19:13,700 --> 00:19:14,500
eshte e nje vajze,

295
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:22,900
e nje motre dhe e nje nene,

296
00:19:23,300 --> 00:19:27,000
qe eshte nje marrdhenie shume shume e paster.

297
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:33,400
Kaq shume sa tani, supozojme qe po e perdorni trurin shume,

298
00:19:33,700 --> 00:19:36,800
atehere pse ju kap ngerci ne zemer - e keni menduar kete?

299
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:41,900
Pse ju kap zemra kur perdorni kaq shume anen tuaj te djathte?

300
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:50,300
Cili eshte shkaku i ngercit te zemres suaj?

301
00:19:50,600 --> 00:19:53,100
Duhet te kuptoni kete, eshte e njejta gje.

302
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:59,700
Marrdhenia e te themi e Shiva ndaj Vishnus eshte ne dy menyra.

303
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:07,000
Se pari Vishnu - grua,motra. Ai ishte martuar.

304
00:20:08,900 --> 00:20:09,900
Mire?

305
00:20:10,100 --> 00:20:13,700
Pastaj kush eshte motra e Shivas?

306
00:20:14,900 --> 00:20:17,400
Motra e Shivas eshte Saraswati.

307
00:20:17,800 --> 00:20:21,000
Nese punon shume tek Saraswati, zemra ka ngerc.

308
00:20:21,500 --> 00:20:22,900
Ajo ka maryadas.

309
00:20:27,100 --> 00:20:29,500
Keshtu zune vend martesat e brendshme,

310
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:31,800
prej se ciles marrdhenia e motres

311
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:37,100
ka funksionuar per te mbajtur maryadat e cakrave tuaja.

312
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:39,700
Nese e kalon kete,

313
00:20:39,900 --> 00:20:41,800
ju papritur shkoni ne te majte ose ne te djathte

314
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:44,500
sepse keni kaluar maryadat e tyre.

315
00:20:45,900 --> 00:20:48,600
Tani kjo marrdhenie moterore ka ekzistuar

316
00:20:48,900 --> 00:20:51,800
edhe ne misherime te tjera;

317
00:20:51,800 --> 00:20:53,700
si Muhamedi

318
00:20:54,300 --> 00:20:56,600
pati nje marrdhenie moterore

319
00:20:57,500 --> 00:21:04,300
me - ne fakt duhet ta themi kete

320
00:21:04,800 --> 00:21:07,500
Motra e tij eshte gruaja e Aliut,

321
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:10,900
por Ajo i lindi atij si nje vajze.

322
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:16,800
Pra mund te lindin si vajze ose si moter.

323
00:21:17,300 --> 00:21:20,400
Ajo u lind si motra e Nanakes, Nanaki.

324
00:21:21,800 --> 00:21:25,200
Ajo u lind si vajza e Muhamedit.

325
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:31,300
Pra mund te jete misherimi i nje motre

326
00:21:32,500 --> 00:21:36,500
ose i nje vajze.

327
00:21:36,900 --> 00:21:43,100
Por vajza dhe motra jane te pafajshme, dliresi e paster.

328
00:21:44,600 --> 00:21:47,300
Tani mendoni kete, qe keta njerez

329
00:21:47,300 --> 00:21:53,900
te cilet s'mund te kuptojne rendesine e dliresise,

330
00:21:54,500 --> 00:21:59,300
si mund te flasin per ligje cfaredoqofte?

331
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:05,300
- sepse "ligje" do te thote maryadas,

332
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:10,900
dhe merr kuptimin e duhur

333
00:22:11,900 --> 00:22:14,400
nepermjet fuqise se Vishnumaya.

334
00:22:15,600 --> 00:22:19,800
Tani ju mund te thoni qe te mos vjedhesh gjene e tjetrit,

335
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:27,300
eshte edhe e padrejte, i perket dikujt tjeter.

336
00:22:27,900 --> 00:22:29,900
Por kush do iu a thote juve?

337
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:33,500
Kush eshte ai qe do ju thote qe kjo eshte gabim?

338
00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:35,800
Sigurisht, ka police, por

339
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,500
kush e ka thene?

340
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:39,300
Ligjberesit.

341
00:22:40,100 --> 00:22:43,500
Ajo pjese e te pandergjegjshmes qe ka luajtur eshte Vishnumaya;

342
00:22:44,300 --> 00:22:47,900
sepse sapo ju vidhni dicka ndiheni fajtore.

343
00:22:49,600 --> 00:22:52,500
Edhe ne ligj eshte perdorur fjala "fajtor".

344
00:22:53,100 --> 00:22:57,700
Dhe faji vjen nga ana e majte, eshte Vishnumaya.

345
00:23:02,100 --> 00:23:06,200
Pra sa e rendesishme eshte te kemi kuptimin (sensin) e dliresise.

346
00:23:06,900 --> 00:23:08,900
Por ne jemi njerez shume te ndare (percare),

347
00:23:08,900 --> 00:23:11,900
ne ata qe kane dliresi morale

348
00:23:11,900 --> 00:23:14,300
dhe ne ata qe mund te mos kene dliresi materiale.

349
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:18,000
Ata qe kane dliresi materiale

350
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:20,500
mund te mos kene dliresi morale.

351
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:24,300
E para vjen dliresia Morale

352
00:23:24,300 --> 00:23:25,700
kjo eshte shume e rendesishme,

353
00:23:25,700 --> 00:23:27,100
sepse eshte e lindur.

354
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:35,700
Dhe nese dliresia juaj morale eshte ushqyer persosmerisht,

355
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:41,900
atehere automatikisht vjen dliresia materiale.

356
00:23:42,700 --> 00:23:44,500
Por efekti eshte i njejte.

357
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:49,000
Nese beni para duke mashtruar ne Sahaja Yoga

358
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:51,400
ose nese mashtroni moralisht,

359
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:53,100
do te kape Vishuddhi i majte,

360
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:57,300
dhe i gjithe problemi do te filloje me Vishuddhin e majte.

361
00:23:57,800 --> 00:24:01,300
Tani te supozojme qe dikush provon te mashtroje ne Sahaja Yoga,

362
00:24:01,600 --> 00:24:04,200
do te marre parate e  Sahaja Yoga

363
00:24:04,500 --> 00:24:05,400
ose dicka te tille.

364
00:24:05,700 --> 00:24:08,900
Menjehere do te kete ngerce ne Vishuddhin e majte.

365
00:24:09,300 --> 00:24:11,900
Sapo te kapet Vishuddhi i majte

366
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:14,500
ai do te filloje te sillet ne nje menyre qesharake,

367
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:16,100
do te tregohet i gjithe ngerci,

368
00:24:16,500 --> 00:24:18,500
Edhe nese do te behesh imoral

369
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:20,600
do te kapet Vishuddhi i majte.

370
00:24:20,900 --> 00:24:25,000
Tani e gjithe pjesa e fajit vjen nga ketu.

371
00:24:25,900 --> 00:24:29,700
Mekat ndaj Nenes mund te jete gjithashtu edhe nje fyerje,

372
00:24:29,900 --> 00:24:32,000
ne cfaredo pergjigje ndaj Nenes.

373
00:24:32,300 --> 00:24:35,900
Kam pare shume njerez qe e kane zakon te thone,

374
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:37,400
"Jo, Nene."

375
00:24:37,800 --> 00:24:40,500
S'duhet te thuhet kurre"Jo",

376
00:24:40,900 --> 00:24:42,200
sepse nese thua "jo"

377
00:24:42,200 --> 00:24:44,500
kjo do te thote te shkosh ne Vishuddhin e majte.

378
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:49,600
Fuqia e Vishnumaya nuk do e toleroje "Jo-ne" tuaj

379
00:24:49,600 --> 00:24:50,900
per asgje.

380
00:24:50,900 --> 00:24:54,300
Shume njerez qe e kane zakon te thone, "Jo, Nene."

381
00:24:55,300 --> 00:24:56,500
Nuk duhet bere,

382
00:24:56,500 --> 00:25:00,600
sepse me tu kapur Vishuddhi juaj i majte

383
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:03,500
gjithe cakrat tuaja te majta behen te dobeta,

384
00:25:03,500 --> 00:25:07,500
per shkak se dliresia qe eshte baza e te gjitha cakrave

385
00:25:08,300 --> 00:25:09,900
eshte e dobet.

386
00:25:10,700 --> 00:25:12,600
Ja pra sa e rendesishme eshte

387
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:18,500
te kuptosh vleren e Vishuddhit te majte.

388
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:20,800
Te gjithe ne te kapur ne Vishuddhin e majte,

389
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:24,900
dhe nuk mendojme se eshte ndonje gje aq e rendesishme.

390
00:25:24,900 --> 00:25:26,500
Por ne themi, "Oh, Vishuddhi i majte po kap

391
00:25:26,500 --> 00:25:27,600
do te thote qe ndihem fajtor."

392
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:30,700
Ne nuk e kuptojme si "Cfare kam bere?

393
00:25:30,700 --> 00:25:33,900
Kam kaluar kufijte, prandaj po shfaqet ketu.

394
00:25:35,500 --> 00:25:38,400
Kam neglizhuar ndonje lloj morali.

395
00:25:38,700 --> 00:25:42,000
Kam shkuar ne rrugen e gabuar kunder Nenes

396
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:45,800
dhe Babait, prandaj po me kap Vishuddhi i majte."

397
00:25:45,800 --> 00:25:50,500
Vishuddhi i majte eshte treguesi i gabimeve,

398
00:25:51,000 --> 00:25:53,500
te keqijave, i mekateve.

399
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:56,100
Ne s'mund ta lejojme qe te kemi Vishuddhin e majte,

400
00:25:56,500 --> 00:25:59,400
Sahaja yogis s'mund te perballojne te kene Vishuddhin e majte.

401
00:25:59,700 --> 00:26:02,300
Si shqetesime shtese, ata pijne duhan,

402
00:26:02,700 --> 00:26:04,300
marrin gjithe llojet te gjerave.

403
00:26:05,300 --> 00:26:10,200
Ne Indi ata marrin ate qe ju e quani tamakhu,

404
00:26:10,500 --> 00:26:14,800
eshte nje lloj- cfare gjethesh jane keto? gjethe duhani,

405
00:26:15,200 --> 00:26:19,600
dhe mendojne se nuk kane gabuar.

406
00:26:19,900 --> 00:26:21,900
Por i kap Vishuddhi i majte.

407
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:26,100
Ne nje fare menyre Vishuddhi i majte eshte kyci (porta)

408
00:26:26,500 --> 00:26:30,300
i te gjitha llojeve te problemeve per veten tuaj,

409
00:26:30,800 --> 00:26:34,600
ndaj jini te kujdesshem te mos ndiheni fajtore per asgje.

410
00:26:35,900 --> 00:26:38,600
Me shume se kjo eshte shume vicioze, rreth vicioz i madh.

411
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:41,500
Per shembull, dikush ka bere dicka te keqe.

412
00:26:42,700 --> 00:26:47,300
Kam vendosur t'ua them atyre ne fytyre

413
00:26:47,300 --> 00:26:49,700
i pelqefte ose jo, kjo eshte gabim,

414
00:26:49,900 --> 00:26:51,800
me shume mundesi. Sigurisht,

415
00:26:51,800 --> 00:26:55,300
ndonjehere perpiqem te luaj ndonje truk me ta qe ta kuptojne,

416
00:26:55,600 --> 00:26:58,800
nese ata s'e kuptojne te thenen Time atehere - vijme ne nje pike.

417
00:26:59,300 --> 00:27:02,800
Dhe une them qe "Tani me mire dilni jashte.

418
00:27:02,800 --> 00:27:05,000
S'mund t'ju kem ne trupin Tim me shume."

419
00:27:05,300 --> 00:27:07,000
Pra i nxjerr ata jashte Sahaja Yoges.

420
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,500
Me t'i nxjerre ata nga Sahaja Yoga te pakten

421
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:10,100
mbaron dhimbja Ime e kokes.

422
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:13,100
Tani kam pare qe

423
00:27:13,300 --> 00:27:18,400
kur fillon te veproje ky negativitet, njerezit,

424
00:27:18,900 --> 00:27:22,300
ne vend qe te perballojne gabimet qe "Une jam gabim,

425
00:27:22,300 --> 00:27:24,900
nuk duhet ta kisha bere kete, eshte gje e keqe per tu bere,"

426
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:27,200
fillojne japin shpjegime.

427
00:27:27,500 --> 00:27:28,900
Kur ju filloni te jepni shpjegime,

428
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:35,900
ky Vishuddhi i majte fillon te behet si nje gunge e madhe e fryre,

429
00:27:36,500 --> 00:27:39,300
dhe atehere nuk ka me mundesi te sherimit,

430
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:41,500
s'ka mundesi te pastrimit.

431
00:27:41,800 --> 00:27:43,500
Pra njerezit fillojne japin shpjegime,

432
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:45,900
"Pse e bera kete, pse e bera ate."

433
00:27:46,100 --> 00:27:48,600
Kur thuhet eshte gabim, eshte gabim;

434
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:49,900
Duhet te pranohet,

435
00:27:50,100 --> 00:27:51,900
"Mire, heres tjeter nuk do ta bej,

436
00:27:52,100 --> 00:27:54,000
Me vjen shume keq." Por "me fal"

