497
00:31:20,300 --> 00:31:23,300
Pra sa me lart te jete nje njeri ne jete,

498
00:31:23,600 --> 00:31:25,500
te zere pozicion me te larte,

499
00:31:25,800 --> 00:31:35,000
me e larte behet ajo qe e quani ego- merr perkedhelje,

500
00:31:35,300 --> 00:31:39,500
me shume e shtyn poshte ne Vishuddhin e majte.

501
00:31:39,900 --> 00:31:43,000
Pra nje person i tille arratiset ne Vishuddhin e majte,

502
00:31:43,300 --> 00:31:45,700
sepse thelle ne zemer,

503
00:31:45,700 --> 00:31:47,900
ne ndergjegjen e tij ai ndihet fajtor.

504
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:51,900
Dhe e gjitha vazhdon si nje faj,

505
00:31:52,500 --> 00:31:54,300
faj ne Vishuddhin e majte.

506
00:31:54,700 --> 00:31:57,900
Dhe kur shkon si faj ne Vishuddhin e majte

507
00:31:58,300 --> 00:31:59,900
behet nje situate e veshtire,

508
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:01,500
sepse nje person i tille,

509
00:32:01,900 --> 00:32:03,700
behet ekstremisht i ndjeshem.

510
00:32:03,900 --> 00:32:06,600
Nje gje ti thuash dhe ai do te ndihet fajtor.

511
00:32:07,100 --> 00:32:09,700
Ti perpiqesh te kurosh Vishuddhin e tij te majte,

512
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:12,000
pastaj ai behet edhe me keq.

513
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:15,400
Eshte nje situate shume e keqe me njerezit e Vishuddhit te majte,

514
00:32:15,700 --> 00:32:19,100
dhe ka njerez qe jane te Vishuddhit te majte te cilet

515
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:20,800
japin gjithmone shpjegime.

516
00:32:21,900 --> 00:32:24,600
Nje person qe ka Vishuddhin e djathte do jete arrogant,

517
00:32:24,900 --> 00:32:28,100
njerezit e Vishuddhit te majte kane nje metode shume dinake

518
00:32:28,100 --> 00:32:32,300
te kthimit te pergjigjes dhe shpjegimeve per cdo gje.

519
00:32:32,300 --> 00:32:33,400
Cfaredo te thoni, ata do te thone,

520
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:35,500
"Jo Nene, kjo eshte keshtu, kjo eshte keshtu."

521
00:32:35,500 --> 00:32:39,200
Kjo eshte nje gje. Jo vetem kjo, s'mbaron ketu,

522
00:32:39,500 --> 00:32:41,200
ju jep sarkazem.

523
00:32:41,900 --> 00:32:45,400
Kjo eshte arsyeja pse njerezit ne Perendim nuk flasin hapur,

524
00:32:45,400 --> 00:32:47,000
gjithmone jane sarkastike.

525
00:32:47,600 --> 00:32:50,200
Ata mendojne se eshte budallallek te flasesh hapur,

526
00:32:50,800 --> 00:32:51,900
s'eshte inteligjente,

527
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:55,500
nese dhe derisa te flasesh ne menyre shume sarkastike

528
00:32:55,900 --> 00:32:58,800
qe e dini ndonjehere eshte shume e veshtire per tu arritur.

529
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:04,200
Kjo eshte menyra e shtrember se si ata flasin.

530
00:33:04,700 --> 00:33:09,500
Dhe kjo pandershmeri vjen prej ketij problemi te Vishuddhit te majte.

531
00:33:09,500 --> 00:33:11,400
Nese Vishuddhi i majte eshte kaq keq,

532
00:33:11,700 --> 00:33:17,100
nuk mund te arrini asgje qe eshte e embel,

533
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:19,000
qe eshte e bukur,

534
00:33:20,500 --> 00:33:22,200
qe eshte e vlefshme.

535
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:26,800
Vishuddhi i majte nuk do te vleresoje kurre.

536
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:28,800
Ata qe vuajne nga Vishuddhi i majte

537
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:31,200
s'mund ta vleresojne kurre personin tjeter, s'munden kurre.

538
00:33:31,900 --> 00:33:34,200
Do te kete fjalen e vet, do te mendoje, "Une jam me i miri"

539
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:36,500
sepse i duhet te ekzistoje,

540
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:39,400
se problemi duhet te ekzistoje, pra si?

541
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:42,300
Eshte nje lloj i egos se semure

542
00:33:42,700 --> 00:33:44,000
qe nuk do te pranoje

543
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:45,600
qe dikush mund te jete me i mire se une,

544
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:47,300
qe me duhet te ndjek dike,

545
00:33:47,600 --> 00:33:50,300
qe me duhet te mesoj nga dikush tjeter.

546
00:33:50,700 --> 00:33:51,900
Kam pasur shume shembuj;

547
00:33:51,900 --> 00:33:53,900
E shoh sidomos tek njerezit qe jane me Mua,

548
00:33:53,900 --> 00:33:57,200
Gjej se ata futen ne Vishuddhin e majte shume shpejt

549
00:33:57,900 --> 00:34:00,800
per shkak te mungeses se protokollit.

550
00:34:00,800 --> 00:34:02,800
Kur fillojne te kene mungese protokolli

551
00:34:02,800 --> 00:34:05,200
ata shkojne ne Vishuddhin e majte.

552
00:34:05,400 --> 00:34:07,800
Pra te jeni me Mua eshte bekim, pa dyshim,

553
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:11,800
por gjithashtu duhet te jesh shume shume i kujdesshem

554
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:14,600
qe te mos e kaloni protokollin.

555
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:17,800
Mos u mundoni te hidheni me perpara,

556
00:34:18,400 --> 00:34:20,100
vetem te krekoseni.

557
00:34:20,700 --> 00:34:25,200
Disa njerez e kane zakon te kapercejne kufijte

558
00:34:25,200 --> 00:34:26,900
dhe sapo ju te kaloni kufijte

559
00:34:26,900 --> 00:34:28,900
krijohet Vishuddhi i majte.

560
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:32,300
Nuk duhet te kete frike per Nenen tuaj,

561
00:34:32,500 --> 00:34:34,200
duhet te kete respekt per Nenen tuaj,

562
00:34:34,200 --> 00:34:38,000
gje qe ruhet nga Vishuddhi juaj i majte.

563
00:34:39,200 --> 00:34:43,400
Tani kjo eshte nje fuqi shume e fshehur e Shri Ganeshes.

564
00:34:43,700 --> 00:34:46,800
Ajo qe e quani se eshte fuqia e Ganeshes

565
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:52,300
eshte Vishuddhi i majte duke vepruar si dliresia.

566
00:34:55,200 --> 00:35:01,700
Fuqite e Ganeshes jane shprehur te gjitha nepermjet Vishuddhit te majte.

567
00:35:03,500 --> 00:35:06,400
Pra ata qe besojne ne Ganesha, ne pafajsine e paster,

568
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:09,200
duhet te dijne qe ne sjelljen tuaj te perditeshme,

569
00:35:09,500 --> 00:35:12,800
ne veprimet e perditeshme,

570
00:35:13,500 --> 00:35:15,000
duhet te kete dliresi.

571
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:19,800
Ganesha eshte shfaqur si lulet e dliresise.

572
00:35:20,700 --> 00:35:24,500
Dhe vetem shihni, nese ne ligjin e hyjnores nuk ka dliresi,

573
00:35:24,500 --> 00:35:26,300
si i kufizoni (caktoni kufijte) njerezit,

574
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:28,600
si i beni mire,

575
00:35:28,900 --> 00:35:30,800
si i pastroni ata,

576
00:35:31,100 --> 00:35:33,000
si i beni ata te evoluojne?

577
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:37,800
Supozojme nje peme po rritet dhe nuk ka kufij ne te,

578
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:40,400
ajo vetem rritet si nje gje e eger,

579
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:41,800
nuk ka ku kufij,

580
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:43,300
me pas cfare do dale nga ajo?

581
00:35:43,300 --> 00:35:44,500
Asgje.

582
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:48,300
Pra per te bere nje person sa me te larte,

583
00:35:48,300 --> 00:35:50,000
