627
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:06,900
Po beni te njejtin gabim perseri e perseri,

628
00:38:06,900 --> 00:38:08,600
dhe ende jeni duke e bere."

629
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:14,300
Duhet ti beni te gjitha injeksionet vetes.

630
00:38:14,500 --> 00:38:17,600
Por ne vend te kesaj fillojne te Me thone,

631
00:38:17,900 --> 00:38:20,900
"Jo, Nene. Jo, Nene. Jo, Nene."

632
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:24,100
